# Fix Mess Details Scroll Position

## Problem
The Mess Details page sometimes opens at a lower scroll position (likely retaining the scroll position from the previous page or not resetting correctly).

## Solution
Explicity scroll to the top of the window when the [MessDetails](file:///c:/Users/barma/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/mess-khojo/client/src/pages/MessDetails.jsx#10-738) component mounts or when the `messId` changes.

## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] [MessDetails.jsx](file:///c:/Users/barma/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/mess-khojo/client/src/pages/MessDetails.jsx)
- Add a `useEffect` hook that triggers on `messId` change.
- Inside the hook, call `window.scrollTo(0, 0)`.

```javascript
    useEffect(() => {
        window.scrollTo(0, 0);
    }, [messId]);
```

## Verification
- Navigate to the Mess Details page from a scrolled-down position on the Home page.
- Verify that the new page opens at the very top.
